@ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7159

### Đăng nhập chủ quán
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "business@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!"
}

### Mua gói — chuyển khoản MB
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/plans/purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": 3
}

### Poll trạng thái
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Admin: đơn chờ
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/admin/payments/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### Admin: xác nhận
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/admin/payments/1/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adminNote": "Da nhan CK"
}
